Cronos II (Scratch) 0.0.4

Cronos II is the open source mail client for the Gnome Desktop.

It features many advanced characteristics that will help
you in your day to day work with your communications and
mailing necesities.

Even though Cronos II is being actively developed and is being
worked by the Cronos II Development Team permanently this is
still BETA software.
Currently is able to handle everything without any problem,
but this does not mean you might find some problem with it.

If you do, please, mail the Cronos II Development Team with
the problems you encountered and every piece of information
you can give so the Team can work to fix your problems.
